### Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/health

### Signup
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User (replace <token> with actual token)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create Memory
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/memories
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: test-key-123

{
  "textContent": "This is a test memory"
}

### Retry Same Request (should get replayed response)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/memories
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: test-key-123

{
  "textContent": "This is a test memory"
}

### Get Memories
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/memories
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Search Memories
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/search?q=test
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get Reminders Inbox
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/reminders/inbox
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Mark Reminder as Read
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/reminders/<reminder-id>/read
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Dismiss Reminder
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/reminders/<reminder-id>/dismiss
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Logout
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer <token>

